MatriMoney{pg}A Game by Lyne Dwyer (@QuestingQueerly){pg}TO PLAY: {pg}You are a working-class hero seeking love and financial security on your morning commute.{pg}Your goal is to marry and reproduce as many times as possible before you get to work.{pg}Each child you produce is worth a monetary reward. {pg}You and your opponent(s) must start driving at the same time. The game is over when one of you reaches the office. 
The player who grows the largest family fortune is the winner!{pg}Who will be able to quit their job and retire comfortably with their newly acquired assets?{Spouses = 0}
"""

