{wvy}V R O O M  V R O O M{/wvy}
NAME EnterCar_Dialogue

DLG 4
DRIVING TIP: Proposing is as easy as driving up to a person or vehicle! Why don't you see if you can get lucky? 
NAME Sign2_(Room3)_Dialogue

DLG 6
"""
You approach the driver and shoot your reproductive shot.{shuffle
  - She winks at you flirtatiously.{pg}"Well hi there, handsome!"{pg}You propose using your handy (reusable) diamond ring - and she says yes! {Spouses = Spouses + 1}{pg}You two are now {rbw}married{/rbw}! You have {print Spouses} spouse(s).
  - She looks you up and down before settling on avoiding eye contact. {pg} "I'm not interested..."{pg}Time to move on. You have {print Spouses} spouse(s).
  - She rolls up the window and pretends not to see you.{pg}Time to move on. You have {print Spouses} spouse(s).
}
"""
